github_body:
General changes:
    * #382 Updating the privacy settings no longer results in a 404.
Map changes:
    * #381 Improved the performance while zooming in/out of the map.
    * #372 Awakened enemies can now be killed with the final boss.
    * #384 You can now change the Teeming state of your map after it's been created.
